title: House of Health
description: A health food, whole foods and bulk foods store that stocks a large range of bulk grains, beans, lentils, rice, flours, pastes, nuts, seeds and dried fruits (many certified organic, bio dynamic and unsulphured and chemical free). Also carries South Australian cold pressed olive oil in bulk, apple cider vinegar, tahini, and tamari. You can also find freshly ground peanut butter (with no added oil, sugar or salt). A wide range of gluten free and vegan products including sweets, raw sweets, pasta, breads, biscuits, sauces and snack foods are also available. Other products include vitamins and dietary supplements including spirulina, barley and wheat grass powders, and a large range of organic and chemical free shampoos, skin care products, toothpastes, and pure essential oils.
